Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] The Second L,\Nand the person I think is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kiyomi Takada from News 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an announcement\Nthat comes directly from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His words are to become\Nthe new law of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can make use\Nof Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] He's removing the bugs?\N-We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kiyomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is... Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SCORN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] All the pieces\Nhave fallen into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that things have come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my turn to go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Rester?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I need you\Nto return to New York immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm intending to go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. So you would like me\Nto stay in New York while you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's the point of me\Ncoming back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, I've never made\Ntravel arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or boarded a flight on my own before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need you to come back,\Nso you can escort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[plane engines roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] We got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Yoshida Productions and NHN\Nare practically begging us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Misa-Misa Comeback Plan\Nwas a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, it's nearly impossible\Nfor anyone to get into NHN,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but this will get us full access.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi will be gaining entry\Nas Misa's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely be to our advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to have someone\Nwho can go in and out freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,\NI'll continue investigating Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-[beeping]\N-[all] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Near. I want to speak to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is L. What is it you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm following through with my goal\Nto arrest Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I'm in Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] L, I presume\Nyou've already contacted Takada
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for the purposes\Nof your own investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[men] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. In fact, I'm investigating\Nher myself at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a given that if we want\Nto get any closer to capturing Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have to keep an eye on\NKiyomi Takada and NHN in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to pass on a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Inform her that as of now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,several SPK members have entered Japan\Nin order to catch and arrest Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But why do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To lure Kira out of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I also want you to mention\Nthe following to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so she'll relay it to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In total, there are only four\Nactive members of the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira won't be able to resist\Nsuch an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing him, he won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, he'll try to kill us\Nbefore we get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I'll beat him\Nat his own game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Beat me at my own game, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you want it,\NI'll accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in Japan, as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll be quite close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? We might even\Nhave the chance to meet face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Well, that'll be something\Nto look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] When that time comes, we'll finish\Nthis Kira matter once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all becoming clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very beginning and even now,\Nit's been a one-on-one fight against L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the battle's just shifted to his heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll come out to play if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only fair, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll find out which of us\Nis truly prepared to win
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and whose wits will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens,\Nthis long battle will end
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can finally begin\Nmy reign at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] First, let's review\Nwhat we know so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,L is Light Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's also Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we'll call him L-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who has the notebook\Nand is currently using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call him X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the pattern\Nof X-Kira's killings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he has definitely made the deal\Nand acquired the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Kira and X-Kira\Ncan't communicate directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be planning to communicate\Nusing Takada as a go-between.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, given the situation as it now stands,\Nthere are two ways to win against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One, the simple way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We arrange to kill both L-Kira and X-Kira\Nand confiscate the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no matter what might happen,\Nwe will never resort to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] That's not the way we work,\NCommander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"We," sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We kill those two and the murders stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Such ex post facto justification\Nwill not be tolerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the way L and I do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that would be an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, L entrusted this case\Nto those who came after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[sounds of traffic]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[car engine revving]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kiyomi, I heard on the news\Nthe other day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that you receive an enormous amount\Nof fan mail every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Yes. I'm told, on average,\Nit's about two hundred letters a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Two hundred letters?\NWow, I'm a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is kind of boring listening\Nto audio only without any video feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should look through them,\Neven if they are just letters from fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] "Keep calm as you read this note\Nand the ones that follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure not to let the people\Nlistening to this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hear your reactions."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The SPK has started\Nto make its move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to start thinking\Nabout your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of only accepting messages\Nfrom Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you should consider making\Na few demands of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Light's getting down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You shouldn't only be\Na spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice should be heard as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Reach out to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him what you think he needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] "I have a different job for T.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to create the perfect world\Nthat Kira has envisioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to begin judging\Nand punishing people as Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you. It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do this, I'm sure\Nyou'll be able to send Kira information
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't want the SPK to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] All right. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-We nailed it.\N-That's our Light for you. He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Delete, delete…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Kiyomi Takada?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone continues ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an important message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to send me a fan letter\Nthat I'll be able to recognize as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You will also enclose something else\Nin the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Five blank pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry on with your judgments\Nand killings as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,until I receive the letter and the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And how about after you receive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop using the real notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you must continue entering names\Nin a fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-A fake?\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a notebook that looks\Nas close to the original as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and act as if you're killing people\Nby using this decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not my place to question God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His will is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to do what God wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat theme music]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the replacement for Kira's Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what's wrong with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[TV host] Welcome to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Ms. Takada will introduce\Nher four new female bodyguards
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who were selected after\Na rigorous screening process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is the winner\Nof the 22nd World Karate Championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Tatsumi Ooyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The second is a former CIA agent,\NMs. Hal Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If there's an SPK member\Namong these bodyguards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it would have to be Hal Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Near's conducting\Nhis own investigation of Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] A phantom killer\Nwho stabbed six people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in Shinjuku's busy quarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Who would I choose\Nto be X-Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,out of all the people in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi on TV] Educating our children\Nabout the existence of Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the meaning of his teachings\Nmust be made mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, we must teach our children\Nthat Kira is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Takada was chosen\Nbecause she's a strong supporter of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that means X-Kira must be someone who knew\Nthat Takada was a Kira-worshipper,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who had a close,\Nintimate relationship with her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,before selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Kira will not forgive any crime,\Nno matter how small.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point onwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you should assume that any person alive\Nis a viable target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense, dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear Kira's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear his thoughts once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should follow his teachings,\Nexactly as Kira ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it's obviously the quickest path\Nto lasting world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,THINKING ABOUT THE RECONSTRUCTION OF JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Youth have a responsibility.\NI think it is of the utmost importance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that young people do all they can\Nto contribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to improve our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are no words or orders from Kira,\Nthen we have only one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to think for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to consider\Nwhat Kira has taught us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,determine what he wants most\Nand make our own decisions from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] L-Kira is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could X-Kira be Teru Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[voices] Kira's Kingdom... Spokesperson...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems to fit into place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] That's what I've been asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, tell me why I'm not the headliner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I was supposed to be\Nthe highlight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of the East-West Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true that you're the highlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to the headliner,\Nit's a little harder to secure that spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[frustrated grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman] That's why we should be\Ntaking precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even realize that Light's\Njust using her for his investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. You might end up dead\Nif she hears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh, I know that.\NThat's why I whispered it quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She snickered at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go kick her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I doing? What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[frustrated grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lidner, that young lady\Nis actually a very good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you shouldn't be\Nso rough with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Miss Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Uh, Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,L, this is Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a small request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Aizawa is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would it be possible for me\Nto speak to him for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, this is Aizawa. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question regarding surveillance\Nfor L and Takada's meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you recording both audio\Nand video feeds of their conversations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, only an audio feed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I see.\NOnly wire taps at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're only using wire taps,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's safe to assume\Nthat L-Kira and X-Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,have found a way to contact each other\Nthrough Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Lidner could be in more danger\Nthan we realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew the risks getting into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To be blunt, what's important is\Nthat L starts focusing his attention
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,on Lidner and Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we'll use the opportunity\Nto investigate Mikami further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things, Gevanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about Mikami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange, it's ridiculously easy\Nto trail him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] He's not trying to hide\Nor anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lived at the same place\Nthe past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing unusual about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He also seems to be totally dedicated\Nto his career as a prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to think he can't be X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there is a very high probability\Nthat Mikami is X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Don't enter his room yet.\NJust keep watch over him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Man, how many meetings\Ndo I need to have with NHN,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for crying out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And, seriously, how many times\Ndo these people have to tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Be careful about what you say"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Yes. Yes, of course.\NI'll ask her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Takada would like to have dinner\Nwith you this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just the two of you.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The music festival's MC should have dinner\Nwith the main performer at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her, "Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Takada, she's accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Lidner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please book a nice private room for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And, also, I'd like you\Nto attend the dinner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Christmas choir singing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Misa, I'm sorry to have\Nto invite you to dinner so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it had to wait until after\Nthe nine o'clock news was finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] No problem. I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a night owl anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gulping wine]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure how to answer\Na question like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Light must be pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you two manage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows that I can't see him that much,\Nwhile she can be with him all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are great between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is way more affectionate\Nthan he looks, at least with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he starts clinging to me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as he gets in the door\Nevery night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're doing well.\NThank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Actually, I should probably tell you,\Nsince you are the MC...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to announce my engagement\Nto Light at the Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he does. It's an engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if I can get engaged\Nto myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He proposed to me more than a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it'd be exciting\Nto announce it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Pop Music Festival, Miss MC?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "if I'm able to"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you not going to let me\Nannounce it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're gonna get Kira to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Kira can decide\Nwho he's going to punish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with his decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've always thought of you\Nas a good friend, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say such terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't have any intention\Nof killing anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how horrible they might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts in frustration]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to really like Kira too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know for sure\Nthat Light's gonna catch him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gulps noisily]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhales] Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he gets caught,\Nit'll be nothing but bad news for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for you, you'll probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Takada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kiyomi. I am the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, join me, Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will be\Nthe goddess of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Kiyomi] Miss Amane?\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I find this unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[huffs] Oh yeah? I feel the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously this was a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've waited until you grew up\Nand learned a few manners
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before I invited you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll know better next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Goodbye.\N-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm older than you, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being childish for storming out\Nin the middle of dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,over a silly little comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa laughs loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opening]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[classical music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Hey, Mochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, Mochi! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Of course, I am. I won, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Won?\N-Yeah. It was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About tonight's meeting\Nbetween Takada and Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they just talked about Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you read between the lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,they were arguing over\Nwhich one was his lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can determine is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami is popular with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that Takada and Amane\Nboth adore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, please be serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] It is serious if they're both\Ntruly in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They will not easily betray him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they'll likely do\Nwhatever he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[train thundering past]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman] Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wearing a short skirt like that\Nin the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] Mikami's just taken out\Na notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[wheels grinding]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's writing something in it.\NCould that be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] He's getting off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[suspenseful music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]